    ('Kali Dal', 'whole urad dal, ghee, cumin, garlic, dry red chilli, asafoetida, turmeric, salt, coriander leaves', 30, 210, 'easy', 'veg', 'comfort', 'north-indian', 'Rinse 1 cup whole urad dal and pressure cook with 3 cups water, 1/2 tsp turmeric and 3/4 tsp salt for 3-4 whistles until soft; Whisk the dal smooth and add hot water to reach a pourable consistency; keep on a low simmer; For the tempering, heat 2 tbsp ghee and add 1 tsp cumin, 4 sliced garlic cloves, 2 dry red chillies and a pinch of asafoetida; fry until golden; Pour the sizzling tempering over the dal; Simmer 5 minutes, finish with chopped coriander and a squeeze of lemon; serve hot with rice or roti'),
    ('Mixed Dal', 'assorted lentils, ghee, cumin, garlic, dry red chilli, asafoetida, turmeric, salt, coriander leaves', 40, 280, 'easy', 'veg', 'comfort', 'north-indian', 'Rinse 1 cup assorted lentils and pressure cook with 3 cups water, 1/2 tsp turmeric and 3/4 tsp salt for 3-4 whistles until soft; Whisk the dal smooth and add hot water to reach a pourable consistency; keep on a low simmer; For the tempering, heat 2 tbsp ghee and add 1 tsp cumin, 4 sliced garlic cloves, 2 dry red chillies and a pinch of asafoetida; fry until golden; Pour the sizzling tempering over the dal; Simmer 5 minutes, finish with chopped coriander and a squeeze of lemon; serve hot with rice or roti'),
    ('Aloo Paratha', 'spiced mashed potato, whole wheat flour, salt, oil, ghee, water', 20, 180, 'easy', 'veg', 'comfort', 'north-indian', 'Knead a soft dough with 2 cups flour, 1/2 tsp salt, 1 tsp oil and about 3/4 cup water; cover and rest 20 minutes; Divide into 6 balls; roll out, stuffing with spiced mashed potato if required, and dust with dry flour; Cook on a hot tawa 1-2 minutes per side, brushing with ghee, until golden brown spots appear and it puffs; Serve warm with curd, pickle or curry'),
