    ('Gulab Jamun', 'milk solids, sugar, ghee, cardamom, saffron, water', 40, 400, 'medium', 'veg', 'comfort', 'sweets', 'Make a smooth batter or dough for the milk solids and rest 10 minutes; Boil 1 cup sugar with 1/2 cup water, 2 cardamoms and a few saffron strands to a 1-string syrup; keep warm; Fry on low-medium heat (about 160C) until evenly golden, turning often; Soak the hot fritters in the warm syrup 15-20 minutes until plump; Rest and serve'),
