    ('Rasmalai', 'chhena and milk, sugar, milk, ghee, cardamom, chopped nuts', 40, 340, 'medium', 'veg', 'comfort', 'sweets', 'Cook the chhena and milk with 2 cups full-fat milk and 1 tbsp ghee on low heat, stirring often so it doesn''t catch; When it thickens, add 1/2 cup sugar and 1/4 tsp cardamom powder; keep stirring 8-10 minutes; Cook until it leaves the sides of the pan and turns glossy; Garnish with 2 tbsp chopped nuts; serve warm or chilled'),
